        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Righteousness, in its widest sense, includes mercy; and so the meaning here may be, \"Thou art good and gracious; of which thy having spared us is a proof;\" or ",
        "children": []
      },
