        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " may have its more usual sense of \"just,\" and Ezra may mean to say, \"Thou art just, and therefore hast brought us to the low estate in which we are to-day, and made us a ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
